data.description: You won't want to miss this stunning 5-bed, 3 full & 2 half-bath home that has been meticulously renovated, offering the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless charm. The fabulous staircase is one of the many captivating features of this home. The gorgeous kitchen will not disappoint along with the spacious family room with built-in shelves around the fireplace. Sunroom overlooks the huge back yard - great for entertaining. Spacious primary bedroom with an AMAZING en-suite bathroom. New windows, newer HVAC, and new lighting throughout. Finished basement for even MORE entertaining space.
